data.description: If you've been looking for a home that feels like a private getaway, 7165 Carey James Road may be the perfect match! Featuring two bedrooms, a loft that can be used as a third bedroom, two full bathrooms, a large living area, one acre of land, and serene views of farmland, this property has so much to offer its future owners. Although this home is located in the small town of Manor, it's still just a short drive to a larger town nearby. One is sure to enjoy the breeze from the upcoming fall nights or a good cup of coffee in the mornings while relaxing on the front porch! Begin your next chapter of life by saying yes to this​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ address.
